sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant EvalAPI as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP<br/>/alpha/eval/*
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod<br/>(retrieve_data + run_ragas)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Inference: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation (in-process)
        Client->>EvalAPI: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>benchmark_id, candidate
        EvalAPI->>DatasetIO: Retrieve dataset rows<br/>(Python in-process call)
        DatasetIO-->>EvalAPI: Dataset rows
        EvalAPI->>Inference: LLM completions via<br/>LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>(Python in-process call)
        Inference-->>EvalAPI: LLM responses
        EvalAPI->>Inference: Embeddings via<br/>LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>(Python in-process call)
        Inference-->>EvalAPI: Embedding vectors
        Note over EvalAPI: ragas.evaluate() runs<br/>metrics: faithfulness,<br/>answer_relevancy,<br/>context_precision,<br/>context_recall
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Job ID (completed inline)
        Client->>EvalAPI: GET /alpha/eval/job/result
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Evaluation scores (JSON)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>EvalAPI: POST /alpha/eval/run_eval<br/>benchmark_id, candidate
        EvalAPI->>KFP: Health check (GET /apis/v2beta1/healthz)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: Healthy
        EvalAPI->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func()<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: Run ID
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Job ID (async)

        Note over KFP,S3: Pipeline execution (async)
        KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pipeline run
        KFPPod->>EvalAPI: Step 1: retrieve_data<br/>GET datasets from Llama Stack<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (no TLS, no auth)
        EvalAPI-->>KFPPod: Dataset rows
        KFPPod->>EvalAPI: Step 2: run_ragas<br/>LLM completions via LlamaStackRemoteLLM<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (no TLS, no auth)
        EvalAPI-->>KFPPod: LLM responses
        KFPPod->>EvalAPI: Embeddings via LlamaStackRemoteEmbeddings<br/>8321/TCP HTTP (no TLS, no auth)
        EvalAPI-->>KFPPod: Embedding vectors
        Note over KFPPod: ragas.evaluate() runs
        KFPPod->>S3: Write results (JSONL)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials

        Client->>EvalAPI: GET /alpha/eval/job/status
        EvalAPI->>KFP: Check run status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        KFP-->>EvalAPI: Run status
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Job status

        Client->>EvalAPI: GET /alpha/eval/job/result
        EvalAPI->>S3: Read results (JSONL)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>EvalAPI: Result data
        EvalAPI-->>Client: Evaluation scores (JSON)
    end
